- obtain mysql source code
- create a scaledb directory under the storage directory
- put mysql/impl/Makefile.am in storage/scaledb 
- put mysql/impl/plug.in in storage/scaledb 
- put libscaledb.so (proprietary library) in storage/scaledb
- create an interface directory inside storage/scaledb 
- put the mysql directory in storage/scaledb/interface
- put the scaledb directory in storage/scaledb/interface
- remove the plugin.in and Makefile.am from storage/scaledb/interface/mysql/impl
- build mysql
- run mysql with LD_LIBRARY_PATH including path to libscaledb.so (proprietary library)
- at mysql prompt INSTALL PLUGIN scaledb SONAME 'ha_scaledb.so'
